            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Genio populi <expan><abbr>Cuiculitanor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Claudius <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Honoratus <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II adiutricis <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>I <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pan</abbr><ex>noniorum</ex></expan> equo <expan><abbr>publ</abbr><ex>ico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>exornat</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> ab <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Antonino <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> Pio in <expan><abbr>quinq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urias</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>adlect</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cirt</abbr><ex>ensis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>aed</abbr><ex>ilis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cuic</abbr><ex>ulitanae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>aug</abbr><ex>ur</ex></expan> exedr<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>m cum statua et <expan><abbr>column</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> marmoreis <lb n="5"/>quam <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Modestus pater suus ob <expan><abbr>honor</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>icatus</ex></expan> sine taxatione promiserat ex decreto <lb n="6"/>Fontei Frontiniani <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> ampliata pecunia sua fecit dedicavitque
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Es sind 2 aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten; Angabe der Breite bezieht sich auf Fragment a; Breite Fragmente b: (98) cm. Zeilenlinien für die Beschriftung. (B): Leglay, AE 1964: Z. 4: exed[ra]m; Z. 5: s[i]ne; Z. 6: pec[u]nia.</p>
            </div>
